title: Coast to Coast AM - August 29th 2009 - Secret Technologies
description:
Secret Technologies

Date:
08-29-09

Host:
Ian Punnett

Guests:
Richard Phillips, Carl Zimmer

Bestselling novelist and physicist, Richard Phillips, discussed his work at the famous Los Alamos National Laboratory and shared a terrifying glimpse into the technologies that lie just around the corner.

In the first hour, science writer Carl Zimmer talked about the bedbug epidemic.
